BehaviourMode - Enum Class in com.weatherSDK.behaviour
When you initialize WeatherSDK in the first time you have to provide a Behaviour mode you want to use.
ON_DEMAND - useful if you desire to get data from the API only once.
POLLING - useful if you need to get data from the API several times automatically during the specified time.

WeatherSDKClientHandler - Class in com.weatherSDK
This is a basic class to initialize the WeatherSDK.
It checks a Map of records of API_KEYS that you provide to manage with several instances.
Use instances to set up multiple profiles to handle with.

You have to use static getInstance() method to start work with the WeatherSDK.
